em>When the beating of your heart</em></div><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><em>Echoes the beating of the drums</em></div><div><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://e3.365dm.com/18/12/750x563/skynews-macron-paris-france_4506457.jpg?bypass-service-worker&20181202110022\" alt=\"Emmanuel Macron (C) with Interior Minister Christophe Castaner (2ndR) and Paris police chief Michel Delpuech (R) arrive at the Arc de Triomphe\"><figcaption class=\"image-description\" contenteditable=\"false\" placeholder=\"Chú thích ảnh (không bắt buộc)\">Ảnh: <a href target=\"_blank\">news.sky.com</a></figcaption></figure></div><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><em>There is a life about to start</em></div><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><em>When tomorrow comes!</em></div><div><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://e3.365dm.com/18/12/750x563/skynews-paris-france-protest_4506449.jpg?bypass-service-worker&20181202105035\" alt=\"Cleaners scrubbed off graffiti reading 'the yellow vests will triumph' from the Arc de Triomph before Mr Macron's visit\"><figcaption class=\"image-description\" contenteditable=\"false\" placeholder=\"Chú thích ảnh (không bắt buộc)\">Ảnh: <a href target=\"_blank\">news.sky.com</a></figcaption></figure></div><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><em>Will you join in our crusade?</em></div><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><em>Who will be strong and stand with me?</em></div><div><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://scontent.fsgn2-4.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/47380569_2201956526688906_5100499347351535616_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&_nc_ht=scontent.fsgn2-4.fna&oh=07c531e3b57a820d397b6f583d2ee9c8&oe=5CA4D45F\" alt=\"Trong hÃ¬nh áº£nh cÃ³ thá» cÃ³: má»t hoáº·c nhiá»u ngÆ°á»i, ngá»n lá»­a, ÄÃªm vÃ&nbsp; ngoÃ&nbsp;i trá»i\"><figcaption class=\"image-description\" contenteditable=\"false\" placeholder=\"Chú thích ảnh (không bắt buộc)\">Ảnh: <a href rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">www.theguardian.com</a></figcaption></figure></div><div styl